      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system recently overhauled with upgraded seals. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in and reduced body roll. Riding on staggered Style 67 wheels with Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires, this example delivers exceptional mechanical grip and linear power delivery. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the powertrain and chassis are dialed for the enthusiast driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
